column2: SELECT    s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, ife.ra, ife.dec, mass.* into mydb.ife_stellarMass_galSpecExtra_dr1#_v2 from mydb.for_bpt as ife      CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq(ife.ra,ife.dec, #) AS near      JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID=s.specObjID     JOIN galSpecExtra AS mass ON mass.specObjID = near.specObjID      WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=# AND  mass.lgm_tot_p5# != # AND  mass.lgm_fib_p5# != #
